§eThe End§r is home to §6Trixite§r, a unique extraterrestrial mineral that when processed can yield §6Plutonium§r, §6Cobalt§r and §6Niobium§r. The Niobium is of great interest as it is a great source for early §3Catalytic Cracking Towers§r.

Due to only the main end island existing, Trixite Ore is a limited resourse.§r Trixite Crystals can also be obtained from an §6Asteroid Mining Ship§r, but it is not recommended.

The §6Dragon Egg§r can also be used to create a Backpack which provides passive §eNight Vision§r, §eStrength 2§r and §eFire resistance§r, aswell as some §eRegeneration§r when on low health.
